  "title": "feat(specs): add playground",
  "body": "goal of this is to replace storybook at term, once it's all working as we expect.\r\n\r\nWhat's currently done:\r\n\r\nAn example done for Breadcrumb using Sandpack for all flavours, using local build to get the package contents\r\n\r\n![Screenshot 2023-12-26 at 17 45 37](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/assets/6270048/81a431cc-db5b-4b68-a187-9db95d8f62e3)\r\n\r\n\r\nWhat still coud be done:\r\n\r\n- Maybe tabs for the examples\r\n- actually differentiate between \"focused widget\" and the regular app\r\n- Maybe \"full screen mode\"\r\n- Maybe see if the \"open in sandbox\" could be made working again (times out now because too many files I believe)\r\n- See if we really need only one example per widget, otherwise design for multiple examples\r\n",
